{"title":"Meronri式平闰年判断","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":0,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-5993","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p><span style=\"\">          有一天，精神失常的我——Meronri听说了一个不太科学又毫无依据的平闰年判断规律“四年一闰，百年不闰，四百年又闰，一千六百年不闰，六千四百年又闰……”</span></p><p><span style=\"\">          尽管Meronri会判断了，但对于过大的年份还是不知所措，所以请你写一个程序，根据这个不太科学的规律来判断在这规律下某一年是平年还是闰年的判断结果是否正确。</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行：一个整数n(n&lt;2^63)</p><p>第二行：一个字符串“pingnian”或“runnian”（不包含双引号）</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一行字符串“Yes!”或“No!”</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>2000<br></p><p>pingnian</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>No!<br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>n&lt;2^63<br></p><p>不只是题目所提到的规律。</p><p>Meronri建议你多想想，</p><p>因为这题真的很水。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}